# Mortgage Domain Guardrails

Must enforce:
- Use `useLoanTransitions` / `transition-loan-status` for status changes.
- Never direct-update `loans.status` or `loan_conditions.status`.
- Keep `loan_timeline_events` append-only (audit/compliance trail).
- Respect phase boundaries (3/4/5/7) when adding logic.
- Borrower data stays user-scoped through RLS-aware hooks.
- Account for LendingPad sync ownership before changing synced fields.
- Never expose borrower PII in logs/UI debug output.
